    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. can u get a bit more specific with the grooming stuff? like, specifically regarding hair and facial features. i have some employees who feel like they have to change their natural look to fit in. what actually counts as \"neat\" or \"conservative\" in a high-stakes setting?",
